latestIgtvVideos.title: Hair Transplant
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hair Transplant(HT) is the only way to fill your scalp with natural hair in case of Baldness. 

FUE HT can be done without General Anaesthesia and without any cuts or sutures. 

The expertise of a surgeon is required since not every case could be ideal for HT. 

You can see your best results in 9 to 12 months after getting HT done. 

In a case where more than 5000+ grafts are required, harvesting grafts from Beard or different parts of body could also be an option.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

Microneedling before prp will open closed pores on your scalp . 

Resulting in increased penetration of prp in to scalp. 

It also will activate body’s natural healing mechanism and can magnify the effect of prp. 

Resulting in denser hair, stronger hair roots, and Thicker Hair.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Is Microneedling Really effective for Hair Fall?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Micro-needling works by activating  Body’s natural healing system.

Derma roller used in the treatment is used to make superficial and controlled  injury on the scalp , by keeping the pressure in check the injury won’t hurt you and will sure give effective results. 

The treatment opens the clogged pores thereby increasing penetration of growth serums applied on the scalp. 

On the day of treatment. You should wash your hair and should not use any hair oil or serum. 

Can do this therapy once in 15 days to see visible results. 

Change your device every 6 months for it to give effective results.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Things to add in Diet to Prevent Hair Fall.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
There are multiple nutrients which are important for hair growth. Some of the important ones are:

Biotin: It is one of the types of vitamin B which helps in strengthening and growing of the hair.
Vitamin A: It has an antioxidant action and it also helps the skin glands produce sebum which has a protective and moisturising effect on the hair.
Vitamin C: It is an antioxidant as well. It also makes it easier for the body to absorb iron.
Vitamin D: It helps to stimulate dormant hair follicles.
Vitamin E: It has potent antioxidant action which helps to reduce oxidative stress in the scalp.

Vitamin B12: Deficiency of this B vitamin has been linked with hair fall as well as premature greying of hair.
Iron: Iron deficiency has been linked to hair loss.

Omega-3 Fatty Acids: They have an anti-inflammatory action which counteracts any inflammation which may be causing hair fall.

Add seeds such as Sunflower, chia and Flax seeds. 
Lentils, zucchini, Chinese Cabbage. Any of these on weekly basis.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Reasons of post Covid Hair Fall
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
1) Physical Stress 

2) Mental Stress 

3)Recovery phase of the body. 

#hairfall#postcovidhairfall#hairtransplantion#hair#wellness#beaut

A reversible condition in which hair falls out after a stressful experience.
The stress pushes large numbers of hair follicles into a resting phase. Within a few months, those hairs can fall out. Types of stress can include surgery, childbirth and serious illness.
